Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.02,0:20:47.43,ED-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}十分足夠了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:50.01,ED-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的  十分足夠了
