Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果要在這裡選個人交往的話 你選誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.19,0:04:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,........................
