Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有我穿著學校的泳褲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算問我們...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛出來還這麼遵守校規啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別管這傢伙了 去搭訕泳衣美女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀喝嗚~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全搭訕不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.19,0:06:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 快說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說了你們也不會生氣吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會生氣 什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:06:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她們都是...
