Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.65,0:13:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暑假已經沒幾天了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要玩到吐出來哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要留下遺憾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
